 />\n之後我就問係咪有高鐵<br />\n佢就話係呀全球最長高速鐵路<br />\n三個鐘到廣州<br />\n仲去到哈爾濱（佢指住東北 我哋全程英文講可能聽錯）<br />\n<br />\n海南島釣魚台我都唔知喺邊 所以唔知佢痈冇畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820ee0990a733bb525a7df4f637793d4e114fdd1","tid":501021,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個大陸妹靚唔靚先</blockquote><br />\n佢幾聰明幾世界女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁即係靚唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n答左你啦, 做人唔好咁絕得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n鬼佬同事形容到佢係非常可愛嘅美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad1550b7fd55e4bfb1e271133ff7e57cafe324c","tid":501021,"uid":71725,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f937978f05879d4140ad503736983a2ba6a8307","tid":501021,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐已移民"},{"pid":"1fcc6fccbb8719e72f936ddc74d21c49473c8823","tid":501021,"uid":25899,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突然問佢佢畫得出個形出黎？佢地理老師應該好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真形咋喎 受過教育嘅基本要識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ebb142b6f06a84c6523be2194ae56e3d2f9a6b","tid":501021,"uid":24080,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"介紹我識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鄉下喎"},{"pid":"bfa474af15e8ed104a813fc852799d48733e89ef","tid":501021,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"冇九段線<i